{"tid":2089884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國眾議院一致通過《香港自治法案》","createTime":"2020-07-02T01:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T03:29:34.000Z","uid":227801,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd97132acaaef643013eba4a32c35b4593adc16","tid":2089884,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:19:23.000Z","msg":"美國眾議院一致通過《香港自治法案》<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院通過《香港自治法案》，容許對參與實施「港區國安法」的中國官員實施制裁，懲罰與他們有業務往來的銀行。方案在眾議院獲一致通過，參議院上星期通過類似法案。根據國會規定，法案須要再交回參議院，通過後送交白宮，由總統特朗普簽署。眾議院議長波洛西表示，「港區國安法」對香港是殘酷和全面的鎮壓，破壞香港的自由，標誌著「一國兩制」死亡。<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-02 08:25:08"},{"pid":"a25cfe2e73191c6f3aa630307c9b40be74e59ee3","tid":2089884,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"有咩內容？"},{"pid":"bc2827a274f679797744a9944cb7729199e8110c","tid":2089884,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:21:34.000Z","msg":"玩鋪勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7a70a32ee5263b7a5cb9387b0012a607dd3a98","tid":2089884,"uid":40521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AqaWMJr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqaWMJr.png&h=bf0874e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LJuHHgO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLJuHHgO.png&h=510d58a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a21cc62892868d9e1dbc30c4cdcc07dc877e3cf","tid":2089884,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991984ec1af05d0ba045c93e8444285a0c0d37b9","tid":2089884,"uid":250254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T01:45:23.000Z","msg":"sources ?"},{"pid":"47582e57935e5f9db02172dcd37c4bcb92335d0c","tid":2089884,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"